<%= render partial: "note", locals: {type: "important", note: "The following steps should be performed in your local development environment."} %>

1. Add Skylight to your Gemfile. Be sure to include it in all of your environments.
```ruby
# Gemfile
gem "skylight"
```

1. Get your setup token from <%= link_to "http://skylight.io/app/setup", "/app/setup" %>.

1. Then run the following commands in your terminal:
```
bundle install
bundle exec skylight setup <setup token>
```
This will automatically generate your <%= link_to "`config/skylight.yml`", "advanced-setup#agent-configuration" %> file.

1. <%= link_to "Deploy your application", "./advanced-setup#deployment" %> to production.
